    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Take your<strong> steak</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it adjust to room temperature, then preheat the oven to 220\u00b0C/ 200\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 7 and boil a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>pasta </strong>to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the<strong> </strong>pasta<strong> </strong>for 7-8 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/rump-steak-with-truffled-mac-and-cheese/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once cooked, drain the <strong>cooked pasta</strong> and save a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/rump-steak-with-truffled-mac-and-cheese/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the pasta is cooked, stir your <strong>cr\u00e8me fra\u00eeche</strong> and <strong>grated cheddar cheese</strong> (save the grated Italian hard cheese for later!) through the drained pasta</p><p>Add a generous splash of <strong>starchy pasta water</strong> and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>\u2013 this is your<strong> cheesy pasta</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/rump-steak-with-truffled-mac-and-cheese/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>cheesy pasta</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> (use individual ones for fancy presentation!), top with your<strong> grated Italian hard cheese</strong> and drizzle over your<strong> truffle oil</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven and cook for 15 min or until bubbling and golden \u2013 this is your <strong>truffled mac & cheese</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/rump-steak-with-truffled-mac-and-cheese/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Whilst the truffled mac & cheese is cooking, chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Combine your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> in a bowl \u2013 this is your <strong>balsamic dressing</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/rump-steak-with-truffled-mac-and-cheese/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Pat your <strong>rump steak[s]</strong> dry with kitchen paper, rub them with <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and season both sides generously with <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Once the pan is very hot, add the <strong>seasoned steak</strong> to the pan</p><p>For rare, cook for 2 min max on each side; for medium-rare, cook for 2-3 min on each side; for medium, cook for 3-4 min on each side</p><p>Once the steak[s] is cooked, transfer to a clean plate to rest</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/rump-steak-with-truffled-mac-and-cheese/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the truffled mac & cheese is almost done, wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and shred finely</p><p>Add the <strong>shredded</strong> <strong>lettuce</strong> and <strong>halved tomatoes</strong> to the bowl with the balsamic dressing and give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is your <strong>balsamic salad</strong></p><p>Slice the <strong>rested steak</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/rump-steak-with-truffled-mac-and-cheese/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sliced steak</strong> with the <strong>truffled mac & cheese</strong> and <strong>balsamic salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
